<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-2599] failure to render file with utf8 CID TT fonts</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2599</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The glyphs in the attached file are not rendered correctly. From Sanyam G. in the user mailing list:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I tried to convert the first page of the attached pdf to image and got the attached resulting output&lt;br/&gt;
Please note This PDF uses UTF8 character set and not ASCII character set.&lt;br/&gt;
For ASCII  character set pdfs it works fine.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description>
